eNCA senior reporter Dasen Thathiah shares more details. Courtesy #DStv403 PIETERMARITZBURG - The war on crime has been escalated in Pietermaritzburg.
KwaZulu-Natal Police Commissioner, Nhlanhla Mkhwanazi, led a raid in gang-ridden parts of the city.
It aimed to flush out those breaking the law, and not complying with lockdown regulations.eNCA senior reporter Dasen Thathiah was there and filed this report in the video above.